{"tid":1638041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【最新】林鄭月娥：現無計劃以緊急法實施其他措施","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:58:51.000Z","uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"07bfbc79eccbae2dfbf3d1bf76dafbdb08fda737","tid":1638041,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥表示，現時無計劃以緊急法實施其他措施。<br />\n<br />\n有傳政府會在緊急法下設禁止蒙面規例後會再施加其他限制，例如禁網，林鄭月娥在出席行政會議前表示，現時無計劃以緊急法再實施其他措施。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，禁止蒙面規例是新政策，需要一段時間才能知道成效，不能說只立例數日後就判斷禁蒙面法無效，最重要是新例能夠產生阻嚇性，而新例亦是針對未成年人士。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，在星期日被捕人士當中，有一成是15歲以下，呼籲社會各界共同遏止暴力，不要為暴力行為撐腰和將這些行為合理化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%8F%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E4%BB%A5%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-022608770.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-022608770.html&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=a7ae8365\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%8F%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E4%BB%A5%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-022608770.html</a>"},{"pid":"e4972f96c9dba6d4ed8265d07cba619f7f48d8ac","tid":1638041,"uid":166405,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:37:06.000Z","msg":"即係有啦屌"},{"pid":"731680e4124d277b3656d205fb146ee76be218d5","tid":1638041,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言, 推到